window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Clive Menard is just an ordinary guy living an ordinary life. But when a talking spider crawls inside his head, things get a lot less ordinary…and people start dying.&nbsp;</p> <p>Could an itsy-bitsy arachnid be behind the killing spree terrorizing Clive’s community? To evade a sharp detective and find a murderer among friends, Clive must shake the cobwebs loose and piece together the puzzle of his life, all without falling prey to a dark force beyond his comprehension.&nbsp;</p> <p>A genre-twisting dark comedy, What Hides Within is an <i>EPIC</i> Finalist and Independent eBook Award Runner-Up for “Best Horror.”</p>"; 
